Having regard to the opinion of the European Parliament  (2),
Whereas a significant proportion of the territory of Sweden suffers from permanent natural  handicaps; whereas Declaration No 37 of the 1994 Act of Accession recognizes that the boundaries of  the mountain and other less-favoured farming areas within the meaning of Article 3 of Directive  75/268/EEC should be delimited without delay;
